<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>* في <span style="color:#950000">"التَّسْهِيل"</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>: ويؤنَّث المضافُ،<span style="color:#006d98"> ثم قال:</span> وقد يَرِد مثلُ ذلك في التذكير، فدلَّ على قِلَّته، قال <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span>:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بَهْجَةُ الحُسْنِ <span style="color:#707070">[فَاتِنٌ]</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٣)</span> فَاغْضُضِ الطَّرْ ... فَ لِتُكْفَى صَيْدَ الظِّبَاءِ الأُسُودَا <span style="color:#008000">(٤)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وقال <span style="color:#008000">(٥)</span>:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رُؤْيَةُ الفِكْرِ مَا يَؤُولُ لَهُ الأَمْـ ... ـرُ مُعِينٌ عَلَى اجْتِنَابِ التَّوَانِي <span style="color:#008000">(٦)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وقال <span style="color:#008000">(٧)</span>:<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِنَارَةُ العَقْلِ مَكْسُوفٌ <span style="color:#008000">(٨)</span> ... ...<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وقال <span style="color:#008000">(٩)</span>:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِسَاءَةُ مَنْ يَبْغِي ... ..... ...<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
